Description:
The package will initialize the Mosquitto to use TSL connection.
Then, subscribe to the MQTT topic.
Once a subscribed message is received, a callback function will be executed. 
Callbak function will parse the payload.
Based on the parsed value, the application will create instance if its record is not found. Otherwise, the applicatio will update the sensor values.

Dependency package:
OpenSSL
Mosquitto

Note:
Please note that the code is under development. It is not yet fully tested and debug.
Hence, it may not compilable.